{"tid":2196342,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"印度男子涉強姦及襲擊86歲祖母被捕","createTime":"2020-09-09T23:13:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-22T08:06:12.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"84bd1ae1536c63c40421ba3038b21eb485e65c5c","tid":2196342,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T23:13:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1548798-20200910.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1548798-20200910.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=8aZ3B%2FsgtJclBbEiVdGGExZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=33153944\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1548798-20200910.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=166a7314\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1548798-20200910.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n印度首都新德里一名30多歲男子，涉嫌強姦及襲擊86歲的祖母被捕。<br />\n<br />\n事發在當地星期一晚，報道說，這名老婦當時在屋外，等候送牛奶的人，但疑犯告知老婦送牛奶的人不會來，並提出帶她去可以取得牛奶的地方，結果老婦被帶到附近一個農場強姦及毆打，路經的村民聽到老婦的哭泣聲後揭發事件，警員到場將疑犯拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n有當地婦女團體形容事件令人非常傷心，又對老婦的經歷感到震驚，形容對方遭受極大創傷，要求判處疑犯死刑。"},{"pid":"4ad4dc181d58becda4ce67778a6cb71a36b876f2","tid":2196342,"uid":245849,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"84bd1ae1536c63c40421ba3038b21eb485e65c5c","tid":2196342,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T23:13:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1548798-20200910.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1548798-20200910.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=8aZ3B%2FsgtJclBbEiVdGGExZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=33153944\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1548798-20200910.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=166a7314\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1548798-20200910.htm?s